querysource.name: dati_udc
querysource.sql: select udcdudc as "udc", udnmdis as "distinta", udcdflg as "stato", sum(punmcpe) as "num_copie", max(data_ora(udtmins)) as "data_ora_ins", max(data_ora('now')) as "data_ora_stampa" from carichi_udc_stor,carichi_prodotti_udc_stor where udcdudc=pucdudc and udcdudc=<? value('udc') ?> group by udc,distinta,stato;

querysource.name: lista_articoli_in_udc
querysource.sql: select u.UDCDUDC as "udc", r.PUCDPRO as "codice", r.PUNMCPE as "quantita", c.PRDSTIT as "titolo" from carichi_udc_stor u,carichi_prodotti_udc_stor r,catalogo c where u.UDCDUDC=<? value('udc') ?> and r.PUCDUDC=u.UDCDUDC and r.PUCDPRO=c.PRCDPRO order by udc, codice;
